metadata.Plot: Workaholic Mike Porter finally takes some time after his affair to mend his ailing marriage with Ashley on a week-long holiday in the Dixie island resort where her family went regularly till her kid sister drowned. It's run by suave Jim Ross with wife Kelsy and ex-con cousin Johnny Vanks as maintenance man with an abusive stepfather trauma. Souvenir shop manager Gordon's rumor reports get Ashley obsessed with the anklet bracelet she found on a pier, which belonged to long-missing maid Beth Campbell, and with local Melanie Kenzer went missing recently, whose fake sister teams up with Ashley suspecting Johnny. Mike feels neglected as this crosses the reconciliation, and spends most time fishing with Jim. .Johnny wrestles with a drug problem, a manipulative dealer on staff Deena and guilty nightmares, unlike his key accomplice.
